{"tid":1014463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為表示願意在波蘭設立網路安全中心","createTime":"2019-02-09T08:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T02:48:57.000Z","uid":141151,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7a7ea610e2e7938eb82d8ae257fe94a626361169","tid":1014463,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T08:12:39.000Z","msg":"華為表示願意在波蘭設立網路安全中心<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/HUAWEI-OFFERS-TO-LAUNCH-CYBER-SECURITY-CENTER-IN-POLAND-20190206/4775073.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2FHUAWEI-OFFERS-TO-LAUNCH-CYBER-SECURITY-CENTER-IN-POLAND-20190206%2F4775073.html&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI69osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=664360bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/HUAWEI-OFFERS-TO-LAUNCH-CYBER-SECURITY-CENTER-IN-POLAND-20190206/4775073.html</a><br />\n<br />\n全球最大的電信設備製造商華為表示，它願意在波蘭建立一個網絡安全中心。<br />\n<br />\n華為波蘭辦事處主任Tonny Bao星期三在一個新聞發布會上說，如果當局接受上述安排為可靠的解決方案，該公司已經準備好在波蘭設立一個網絡安全中心。<br />\n<br />\n華為的另一位官員也在發布會上表示，波蘭政府沒有理由將中國公司排除在它未來的5G網絡發展計劃之外。<br />\n<br />\n今年一月，波蘭以間諜罪指控逮捕了華為的一名中國僱員和一名前波蘭安全官員。"},{"pid":"1aa3baa921ab4ee7c2d8b8dc1922bc78e3034d3e","tid":1014463,"uid":28397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T08:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5d697465b829d37111e7466546170ca7cef703","tid":1014463,"uid":81113,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T08:25:59.000Z","msg":"仲比你設立間諜中心？<br />\n<br />\n當人傻架？"},{"pid":"f693ffa0189c54cd97eaf59cd888ef896fe074c8","tid":1014463,"uid":121146,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T08:28:54.000Z","msg":"安全？點安全法？"},{"pid":"7056442658796f7887dccf2a387b7930dfa71868","tid":1014463,"uid":30633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy"